\bibitem{FOOTV} This is consistent with a scalar field source
$\Phi=\Phi(z)$, for which
$T^{\mu}_{\;\;\nu}=
 v\delta^{\mu}_{\;\;\nu}+  k (\delta^{\mu}_{\;\;\nu}+2n^{\mu}n_{\nu})$,
where $n^{\mu}\equiv\pm A^{-1/2}\delta^{\mu}_{\;\;z}$, and
